prompts.frontCover: A fantastical beach scene in a flat 2D illustration, dreamy fantasy art style. In the center, cartoon versions of Lao Lao (person on left) and Jordan (person on right) are building a magnificent, whimsical sandcastle together. Jordan is holding a small pail and shovel, laughing as he adds a turret to the castle. Lao Lao is seated beside him, smiling warmly as she carefully places a seashell on top of the tallest spire. They are wearing the same clothing from the reference photo, but without any logos. The sandcastle is impossibly grand, with shimmering, translucent towers and magical glowing windows. The beach sand is a soft, pastel pink, and the ocean waves are a gentle, swirling mix of turquoise and lavender with sparkling sea foam. In the sky, fluffy clouds are shaped like birthday cakes and party hats, all set against a soft sunset gradient of orange, pink, and purple. Several charming cartoon dogs, representing Jordan, are comically "helping" build the sandcastle, with one wearing a tiny hard hat and another chasing a magical, glowing butterfly. Centered in the sky above the couple, the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script using a shimmering gold color.
